Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,A,,0,0,0,,# The Magic Show 魔術秀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,A,,0,0,0,,## On Your Knees 給我跪下
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,A,,0,0,0,,### 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:10.24,A,,0,0,0,,### 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:12.38,A,,0,0,0,,聚過來，給個看\NGather round, take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:14.41,A,,0,0,0,,說說你看到什麼\Ntell me what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:18.49,A,,0,0,0,,寶貝你竟然跑來這樣對我\NBaby now you've gone and done it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:21.24,A,,0,0,0,,你看穿我眼睛沒？\NCan you read my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:23.61,A,,0,0,0,,有個什麼叫著你\NThere's something calling you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:28.13,A,,0,0,0,,我有些魔法你非常的感興趣\NI've got some magic that you'll be really into
Comment: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:28.14,A,,0,0,0,,### 間奏
Comment: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:46.93,A,,0,0,0,,### 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:49.08,A,,0,0,0,,噢...就是這樣\NOhh, just like that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.14,A,,0,0,0,,我把你鉤住的眼神\NThe way I got you watching
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.56,A,,0,0,0,,你有否被催眠過？\NHave you ever been hypnotized?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:56.26,A,,0,0,0,,有否過如此著迷？\NHave you ever been so enticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:58.44,A,,0,0,0,,你不懂這種的魔法\NYou don't know this kind of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:00.79,A,,0,0,0,,就退下讓我發功\Nso sit back and let me work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.11,A,,0,0,0,,來，歡迎來到魔術秀\NSo welcome to the magic show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:04.86,A,,0,0,0,,你會一見鍾情\NIt's love at first sight
Comment: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:05.19,A,,0,0,0,,### 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.46,A,,0,0,0,,所以你就給我跪下\NSo get right down on you knees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:10.18,A,,0,0,0,,你想求饒也是可以\Nand you can beg if you please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:13.88,A,,0,0,0,,喔...噢，沒關係\NOhhh, oh, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.78,A,,0,0,0,,好好活滿你的性命\NAnd live your life to the full
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.53,A,,0,0,0,,別把自己變成蠢蛋\NJust don't make yourself a fool
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:23.53,A,,0,0,0,,噢，歡迎來到魔術秀\NOh, welcome to the magic show
Comment: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:23.66,A,,0,0,0,,### 間奏
Comment: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:51.58,A,,0,0,0,,### 主歌-3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:54.03,A,,0,0,0,,我看來怎樣？看著還好嗎？\NHow do I look? Do I look alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:56.41,A,,0,0,0,,跟我說我漂亮，很迷人\NTell me I'm pretty, a lovely sight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:02:00.66,A,,0,0,0,,我這一生都是照他們想要的那樣\NAll my life I've been told the way they want
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.28,A,,0,0,0,,心中有一股火焰\NFeel a burning in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:05.39,A,,0,0,0,,已不想期盼\NWaiting eyes are out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:09.43,A,,0,0,0,,你真的跑來速戰速決\NNow you've really gone and done it in bout
